ilm)|L.A. Confidential]]'' ‡ || [[Andy Nelson (sound engineer)|Andy Nelson]] (re-recording mixer), [[Anna Behlmer]] (re-recording mixer), [[Kirk Francis]] (production mixer) |- | ''[[Men in Black (1997 film)|Men in Black]]'' || Lee Dichter (re-recording mixer), [[Skip Lievsay]] (re-recording mixer), Michael Barry (re-recording mixer), [[Peter Kurland]] (production mixer) |- |}
